Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Republicans solid for Reagan
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w2nx
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 8 Jun 1980
For once, the Republican party is solidly united for one candidate while the Democrats lose backing for both Carter and Kennedy. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less